{"tid":603533,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有圖 好奇一問","createTime":"2018-03-23T22:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T04:48:12.000Z","uid":167917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ee5fb31b78db0667af06a6d7874d70e76fc8b429","tid":603533,"uid":167917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T22:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/063802_950c8e7f212a2b810575c9c65ee44ace.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F063802_950c8e7f212a2b810575c9c65ee44ace.png&h=b8d1e6c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實啲食肆神咁早送貨又未開鋪<br />\n就咁掉唒喺門口岀面<br />\n哩張相都算好了<br />\n見過有河粉就咁用個薄既袋袋住，放喺地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔怕有廢老拎左去？<br />\n唔怕有老鼠、蟑螂、昆蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecabb0aec22cd1ab43b3438271460d506a4ea308","tid":603533,"uid":102190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T22:44:41.000Z","msg":"你依家先知啲野食咁污糟啊?"},{"pid":"f84d9b71c735f90de67c80a92f7d9cb61b327a6b","tid":603533,"uid":28007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T00:03:41.000Z","msg":"河粉果啲大多數都有個紙箱裝住喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朝早又無人 啲廢老拎到咪拎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n況且拎到都食唔曬咁多啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：做緊廚房"},{"pid":"b6225e8cc6ebb26e406be1524e9bb35839b994f5","tid":603533,"uid":167917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f84d9b71c735f90de67c80a92f7d9cb61b327a6b","tid":603533,"uid":28007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T00:03:41.000Z","msg":"河粉果啲大多數都有個紙箱裝住喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朝早又無人 啲廢老拎到咪拎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif